#ident	"@(#)bnu.admin:Helpbnu	1.1"

ABSTRACT:Basic Networking Utilities Management
	The basic_networking menu provides administrative access 
	to the various files that control the operation of the
	Basic Networking Utilities.  The utilities directly
	affected are the uucp family of commands, including uucp,
	uuto, and cu.  Other commands, such as mail, that 
	communicate with remote systems are also affected by
	basic_networking.

